titleStmt.title: Legenden om Barlaam och Josaphat : Holm A 49 : A digital transcription

availability.p: Licence accepted by Maria Arvidsson in 2015.

projectDesc.p: This manuscript text has been encoded according to the standard set out in The Menota handbook (version 2.0 beta), at http://www.aksis.uib.no/menota/guidelines as of 2004-06-26.

correction.p: This text has been proofread by Karl G. Johansson, University of Oslo.

normalization.p: This text has been encoded on a facsimile level.

interpretation.p: The complete text has been lemmatised according to the rules specified in ch. 8 of the Menota Handbook, v. 2.0.
